headlines.description: — Scottie Barnes had 23 points and six rebounds before leaving with a sprained right foot and the Toronto Raptors beat the Washington Wizards 134-98 on Friday night to finish 4-0 in the preseason.
headlines.shortLinkText: Scottie Barnes scores 23 points, sprains foot in Raptors' win over Wizards in preseason finale

events.name: San Antonio Spurs at Golden State Warriors
